  "prompt_text": "Image-to-video of a green-screen crew layer only. The input image shows exactly seven astronauts in blue flight suits, seen from behind on a pure flat chroma green background. Preserve exactly seven people. Preserve their back-view orientation. Over 8 seconds, they begin upright natural first steps away from camera toward an unseen shuttle pad. Use calm natural walking cadence, not slow motion. Start from the standing pose and step forward without dipping. The seven people should move with slight staggered timing; each person has an independent stride. Keep arms low with only small natural walking arm movement. Keep heads and torsos upright. Keep bodies facing away from camera. Keep feet and legs believable. Keep the background pure chroma green and blank. No camera movement. No time stretching. No squat. No crouch. No knee dip. No bobbing. No slow motion. No marching. No synchronized stride. No waving. No saluting. No pointing. No raised hands. No running. No jumping. No dancing. No turning around. No faces. No readable logos. No name patches. No text. No extra people. No missing people. No duplicated people. No smoke. No fire. No launch. No sparks. No atmosphere effects. No pad background. No floor detail. No props. Pipeline intent: Baseline one-stage q8 I2V, true duration, no stretching.",
